@inherits Atoll.Routing.AtollPageSlice
<h1 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">About This Blog (Razor)</h1>
<p>
    This is a sample blog page authored with <strong>Razor Slices</strong> using Atoll's
    <code>AtollPageSlice</code> base class. It demonstrates that Razor-authored pages participate
    fully in the Atoll routing and SSG pipeline.
</p>
<h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">About Razor Slices in Atoll</h2>
<p>Razor Slices integration brings:</p>
<ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
    <li><strong>Razor templates</strong> &mdash; Author components with familiar <code>.cshtml</code> syntax</li>
    <li><strong>Strongly-typed models</strong> &mdash; Compile-time validated props via <code>AtollSlice&lt;TModel&gt;</code></li>
    <li><strong>Full pipeline participation</strong> &mdash; Slots, layouts, islands, CSS scoping, SSG</li>
    <li><strong>Incremental adoption</strong> &mdash; Mixed C#/Razor component trees work seamlessly</li>
</ul>
